======
 IDLE 
======
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

show how long a user or channel has been idle

| 


| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *idle (st)*

    :description: idle [<nick>] .. show how idle the channel is or show how idle <nick> is

    :permissions: USER .. WEB .. CLOUD

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !idle
        <output> nobody said anything on channel #test yet



    ::

        <user> !idle test
        <output> i haven't seen test


